extendedInfo.description: 80 levels, for Full version of "Space Physics".Install and "LAUNCH" it to unleash resources to SD card. Then uninstall it to free space.*******ATTENTION*******Only for Full version.This is a resource pack, not a game.It's used to store large resources on SD card to free more space for your phone.

reviews.title: Hilarious seeing some dimwits below giving....
reviews.comment: this app a bad rating. Obviously too stupid to understand that the deliberate uninstall after installation is a good feature, saving you RAM once it has been transferred to SD card (the main game app reads it from THERE, not from RAM). By the way, for those having problems getting it to work, you need to remember to OPEN the Pack at least once, before it can be uninstalled. It is when it is opened, that it actually gets copied to your SD card. Also, remember that this is for the full/ PAID game, not the lite/ free version. I hope I\'ve helped!
